COMPILE:
-- The source files can be compiled on both Linux and Windows.
-- The attached executable file (under the bin directory) is built on windows using Code::Blocks 10.05.

USAGE:
-- run the executable file (under bin directory) in windows command line:
lexAnalyst.exe pascal_file_name
-- check the output in console

SAMPLE TEST:
-- example_output.txt is the redirected output by executing "lexAnalyst.exe example.pas > example_output.txt" in Windows command line.
